Name: Math Tile
About the game: The new tile will appear on the top of the box.Change the position of the tile and make it down.If the sum of numbers on a column or row is equal to 5 10 or 20,they will merge together.When two 5 10 or 20 tiles touch, they will also merge into one. feature: · Use right or left key to move the top tile. · Use up key to change the position of the top tile number. · Use down key to put the tile down.
